Summary: Red/orange globes traveling at about the speed of a jet
divs: sighting detailssitting in my backyard in wayne michigan, looking at a full moon. suddenly cloud cover came over the moon. i observed several red\ orange orbs ~ 30 , exit the clouds flying in a straight line at about the speed of a jet air plane.
